--- stdout ---
Options for: find
Available arguments:
          --search : [default] Text to search.
             --tag : Tag sought on the notes.
        --notebook : Notebook containing the notes.
            --date : Date or date range.
           --count : How many notes to show.
Available flags:
         --content : Search by content.
     --exact-entry : Search exact entry.
            --guid : Show GUIDs.
--ignore-completed : Only unfinished reminders.
  --reminders-only : Only notes with reminders.
    --deleted-only : Only deleted notes.
   --with-notebook : Show notebook names.
       --with-tags : Show tags.
        --with-url : Show web URLs.
